{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6d7848eef0","title":"毛泽东会见法国外长舒曼谈话节选","origin":"根据中央文件翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d7f62d413e","index":0,"year":1972,"month":7,"day":10,"articleId":"6d7848eef0"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7c95639aa8","type":"title","text":"毛泽东会见法国外长舒曼谈话节选","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"2d136028d3","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我这个人名誉不好。杜勒斯骂我比希特勒还希特勒。苏联也骂我，叫作教条主义。你看我怎么得了呢？","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"8a3d4a099a","type":"paragraph","text":"舒：我自己过去学过历史。毛主席在世界的历史上能找到没有挨骂的伟人吗？伟人总要挨骂的，否则就不是伟人了。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"cead8ad7b7","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我不算伟人。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"6c02f2028d","type":"paragraph","text":"舒：你自己证明你是伟人，因为尽管有各种人骂你，你还是继续完成了伟大的事业。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"5907ff5f27","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：没有完成多少。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"c7ecb5ca4a","type":"paragraph","text":"舒：改变了世界。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"166efe6c4a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：没有改变多少，改变了一点，十个指头改变一个指头。把这个北京改了一改。最近我们又把一个姓林的，叫林彪，也把他改造了。（笑）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"a4eab05207","type":"paragraph","text":"总理（笑）：不知你听说了没有。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"7c3de9a64a","type":"paragraph","text":"舒：听说了这个人。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"60aba6e02b","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（对总理）：你们要发一个通知。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"c2cb4c4af5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：看到文件了，在搞。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"c6d7884ba4","type":"paragraph","text":"主席（对舒）：这个林彪啊，他天天吹我，说我怎么了不起。而实际呢？就要杀我的头。跟他斗争了几十年，后头变成了“亲密战友”、“副统帅”。他专了两天半的政。我们开了那个庐山会议，1970年8月23日一天，24日一天，25日半天。第三天的下午，我就说不行了，不能干了，下了一滴酒精。一滴酒精下去，细菌就不活动了。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"4d7e10ac85","type":"paragraph","text":"舒：这就看出这滴酒精的威力了。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"},{"id":"c1ce4bcfbc","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：结果庐山会议到去年，1年多，他就呆不住了。谁也没有赶他，谁也没有料到他会跑，坐一架飞机就上天了。他想到苏联去。现在中国人骂他作卖国贼！他反对我们跟美国接近，跟你们西方接近。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0"}],"page":{"id":"a82a8b6d54","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6d7848eef0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}